</tr><tr><td class="hlist" style="padding:0 0.1em 0.4em;padding:0 0 0.6em;">
<div class="NavFrame collapsed" style="border:none;padding:0"><div class="NavHead" style="font-size:105%;background:transparent;text-align:left"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Tibetan_Buddhism" title="Tibetan Buddhism">Tibet</a></div><div class="NavContent" style="font-size:105%;padding:0.2em 0 0.4em;text-align:center"><div class="hlist "><b>Traditions</b><br/>
<ul><li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Sakya" title="Sakya">Sakya</a>
